reakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.","title_alternative":"MacBook Pro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","stars":3133,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":10,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":308985,"username":"kuyuzhiqi","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kuyuzhiqi","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40d34c01993f1eb5990e11e369ff8475?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40d34c01993f1eb5990e11e369ff8475?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40d34c01993f1eb5990e11e369ff8475?s=73&d=retro","created":1523847623,"last_modified":1653695082},"last_reply_by":"kuyuzhiqi","last_touched":1659326319,"title":"等 m2 pro 还是直接上 m1 max？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869895","created":1659323512,"deleted":0,"content":"去年是 10 月发布的 m1 pro ，但拿到电脑要很久，不知道今年会不会发布，没电脑用了","content_rendered":"<p>去年是 10 月发布的 m1 pro ，但拿到电脑要很久，不知道今年会不会发布，没电脑用了</p>\n","last_modified":1659323512,"replies":10,"id":869895},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960","name":"car","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960","title":"汽车","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","topics":1340,"footer":"","header":"关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Car","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","stars":1315,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":176,"parent_node_name":"life"},"member":{"id":244239,"username":"hzzz0823","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hzzz0823","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=73&d=retro","created":1500891216,"last_modified":1500891216},"last_reply_by":"wfd0807","last_touched":1659327073,"title":"求推荐车， 15 以内","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/869901","created":1659324236,"deleted":0,"content":"个人信息：\r\n南京，没车位，孩子 1 岁。\r\n\r\n用车场景:\r\n1. 通勤就 1 公里，应该不会用\r\n2. 带老婆孩子中短距离玩\r\n3. 过年过节回老家（农村），100 多公里\r\n\r\n\r\n预算: 10 万以内有满意的最好… 没有就 15 内也可以，再超个一两万也行。（就必须打住了不然直接库里南了）\r\n\r\n一些偏好和疑问:\r\n1. suv ，感觉空间大点方便。\r\n2. 不考虑纯电（家里唯一的车，好像都不推荐是纯电）。\r\n2. 二手挺好的，但是不知道上哪买… 那些二手 app 可信吗？\r\n3. 因为保值率问题，计划开稍久一点（类比二手 iphone7p 用到前年，好像用了 4,5 年了）。所以担心电车或混动，会不会相比油车不够成熟，开久了出问题和维修花钱比较多？\r\n4. 一些 360 之类的辅助功能，想要，但不知道值不值。（因为刚拿驾照）如果后期可有可无的话，那前期忍一忍，把这笔钱省下来买点电子产品是一个明智的选择吗？\r\n\r\n谢谢！","content_rendered":"<p>个人信息：\n南京，没车位，孩子 1 岁。</p>\n<p>用车场景:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>通勤就 1 公里，应该不会用</li>\n<li>带老婆孩子中短距离玩</li>\n<li>过年过节回老家（农村），100 多公里</li>\n</ol>\n<p>预算: 10 万以内有满意的最好… 没有就 15 内也可以，再超个一两万也行。（就必须打住了不然直接库里南了）</p>\n<p>一些偏好和疑问:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>suv ，感觉空间大点方便。</li>\n<li>不考虑纯电（家里唯一的车，好像都不推荐是纯电）。</li>\n<li>二手挺好的，但是不知道上哪买… 那些二手 app 可信吗？</li>\n<li>因为保值率问题，计划开稍久一点（类比二手 iphone7p 用到前年，好像用了 4,5 年了）。所以担心电车或混动，会不会相比油车不够成熟，开久了出问题和维修花钱比较多？</li>\n<li>一些 360 之类的辅助功能，想要，但不知道值不值。（因为刚拿驾照）如果后期可有可无的话，那前期忍一忍，把这笔钱省下来买点电子产品是一个明智的选择吗？</li>\n</ol>\n<p>谢谢！</p>\n","last_modified":1659324575,"replies":9,"id":869901},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1656605007","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1656605007","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":50070,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007","stars":7916,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":373258,"username":"tysb777","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tysb777","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null